dataList.content: So now that I had some time to look around out here...
This facility appears to be... a gift factory.
I see... so there are factories like these that produce gifts.
... There's still some time until Christmas, though.
Sinclair looked to the ground with a somber expression.
... I didn't need to ask to know how he was feeling.
I wonder if monsters exchange gifts with each other?
They didn't seem like the most hospitable sort.
There is a possibility that they may be contractors to one of the Wings in the City.
I wanted to say 'no chance', but... the City and the Wings that we've experienced so far were...
... Yeah. There was a non-zero chance of that being the case.
